Maabaho wanhu hawengizigwe ulungwana kwaviya womtenda Malagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'hile Musa, wawo wondawamtaguse na kuwatagusa mweye, ingawa mweye mumtenda ulungwana na mwovimanya Malagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'higwe muna Yamalagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'higwe muna Yamalagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'higwe muna Yamalagilizo ya Mulungu yoyamwing'hile Musa.
Kwaviya munhu yoyose iyo Muyahudi kwa kunze siyo Muyahudi, na ulungwana wa kweli siyo ulungwana wa kunze muna dileme hebu wa chiunhu.
Mbali munhu iyo Muyahudi ni Muyahudi iyo yeli mgati, na munhu yondayamwing'higwe ulungwana wa kweli ni chinhu cha muumoyo, mbuli ya Muhe wa Mulungu, na siyo chilagilo chochandikigwe muna Yamaandiko Yelile. Munhu iyo hatogoligwa na wanhu bule, mbali Mulungu.
Maabaho kuna chinhu chilihi chinogile cha kuwa Muyahudi, hebu kuna chinhu chilihi chinogile cha kufungigwa ulungwana?
Kwa chila nzila kuna faida, mwanduso wose, Wayahudi wahuwila Mbuli ya Mulungu ni kweli kumwawo.
Vino izakuwaze one wanhu wamwenga wakala wabule uhuwilo? Vino uhuwilo wawo haudaha bule kumbananga Mulungu kuwa uhuwilo wawo?
Pai! Bule! Hata ivo Mulungu yawoneka kuwa kanoga, hata fana munhu yoyose viyowoneka kuwa mvwizi, Maandiko Yelile yolonga, "Iviya muladi kulonga kwako kwize kulagusa kuwa kolonga kweli, na uhokele muna inhaguso."
One yehile yetu yochilondeka kulagusa viya Mulungu viyolonda wanhu wanogile haulongozi wake, lelo chilonge choni? Vino nolonga choni? Vino Mulungu kochiwonela ludoko kwa kuchitenda chiya chihile? Vino nolonga kwa kuwalongela wanhu muhala.
Siyo ivo bule! One Mulungu kodahaze kutagusa wanhu wa isi yose?
Munhu yoyose kodaha kulonga, "One mbuli zangu za uvwizi zolagusa ukweli wa Mulungu kwa ichimu chake, habali notagusigwa kuwa nina uhasanyi?"
Lelo habali sekechilonge, fana wanhu wamwenga viwolonga, "Chite chiyatende yehile muladi yanogile yeze?" Wawo walondeka yatagusigwe.
Ivo lelo chilongeze, vino cheye chofaya kumfosa wawo? Bule! Kwaviya chiwalongela malagilizo yose kuwa Wayahudi wose na wanhu weli siyo Wayahudi wose wakala muna uufalume wa uhasanyi.
Fana Maandiko Yelile viyolonga, "Habule munhu yoyose yanogile habule hata imwe.
Habule hata imwe yeli na ubala, habule hata imwe yomzahila Mulungu.
Wose wabaguka, wose wabananga, habule hata imwe yoyotenda yanogile, habule hata imwe."
"Mavungu yawo ni fana maleme yoyalagusigwe wazi, kwa lulimi lwawo wolonga vinhu vihile. Mulomo wawo wolonga vihile fana mazoka."
"Milomo yawo imema maligo na wihi."
"Magulu yawo yoha himahima kutowa damu.
