Ivo ndugu zetu, chizalonga choni? Vimuiting'hana hamwe hamwe, chila munhu kodaha kwimba wila, hebu mafundizo, hebu mbuli za Mulungu zoyalagusigwe na Mulungu, hebu mbuli za kulonga kwa ulonzi umwenga, hebu munhu yotaza kulonga, yano yose yatendeke kwa ichimu cha kuzenga bumbila da wahuwila.
