Wamwenga wawo walawa kumwetu, mbali hawakalile wanhu wetu bule. One wahayawile wamwenga kumwetu, wahadahile kukala na cheye. Mbali walawa kumwetu muladi yavimanye kuwa habule munhu yoyose kumwetu yoyakalile kweli.
